content: Headlights May Flicker or Shut Off

Honda (American Honda Motor Co.) is recalling certain 2018-2025 CB300R motorcycles.  The headlights may flicker or shut off while driving.Loss of headlight illumination can reduce visibility, increasing the risk of a crash or injury.

Number of Units Affected: 7212.0
